title: HP'S Multi Jet Fusion is a "Breakthrough for 3D Printing Industry"
text:
HP'S Multi Jet Fusion is a "Breakthrough for 3D Printing Industry" 30 September 2015 Expand HP's J.Scott Schiller on Multi-jet Fusion The first interview from TCT Show + Personalize 2015 comes from one of our keynote speakers, HP's Worldwide Director of 3D Printing, J. Scott Schiller. 
Scott goes into detail about how the company's Multi Jet Fusion Technology will be a breakthrough for the 3D printing industry and when we can expect to see the machines in the wild. 
To keep up-to-date on all the latest videos from TCT Show make sure you subscribe to our YouTube channel . Tags
